{"tid":2352141,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"露營撚 呢排有去露營既入一入黎","createTime":"2021-01-03T20:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T04:27:37.000Z","uid":67910,"like":636,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"96509a9da3e337e586d31b77257fdf6c34b3eb91","tid":2352141,"uid":67910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:10:57.000Z","msg":"本身玩露營都唔係話玩左好耐<br />\n但疫情影響 大家都冇得出去旅行<br />\n好多人都選擇係香港親親大自然 露營<br />\n但麻煩各位有返啲公徳心 對大自然對動物對大家好啲<br />\n<br />\n前排經過赤徑已經見到成個樹林都係口罩<br />\n柯完屎尿又唔撚扔返啲紙巾係想點撚樣？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xtoMdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xtoMdW.png&h=4a88623f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻煩大家最基本拾返自己用過既紙巾<br />\n<br />\n另外露營用品 我理得你係個營又好張椅定張枱<br />\n爛撚左唔該你地自己帶返出市區先扔<br />\n郊外好多清潔姐姐係幾個星期先清理一次垃圾桶<br />\n你地成個營都可以放落垃圾桶 係咪想拎撚死人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDMNttG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDMNttG.png&h=1a026a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有啲樽裝水 壓扁先好放落垃圾桶 有水源既就拎水唔好又做多件垃圾出黎係郊外<br />\n<br />\n仲有天氣涷又好 要氣氛都好<br />\n唔好砌呢啲會燒爛草地既所謂營火<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGzGxWG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGzGxWG.png&h=6495276f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n草地用火燒禿左要用時間慢慢生長 仲要俾你班仆街燒到一個個黑色lone 牛連草都冇得食 <br />\n<br />\n自己制造出黎既垃圾就自己扔返 唔好見個垃圾站滿哂仲繼續放落去 好多野豬同牛會係垃圾站搵野食 食哂啲膠袋 <br />\n呢幾個月實在見到太多好撚過份既人去露營 <br />\n真係好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n 最後 <br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">請帶走你的垃圾 可以的話 請帶走更多垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"4112c77288ac4a12903ebc8820e11e126646b80b","tid":2352141,"uid":70878,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:14:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾帶出市區扔是常識吧"},{"pid":"7055aa0274683504a910535cd08bc7d4fe6059d6","tid":2352141,"uid":67910,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"4112c77288ac4a12903ebc8820e11e126646b80b","tid":2352141,"uid":70878,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:14:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾帶出市區扔是常識吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:26:27.000Z","msg":"如果每個人都好似你咁諗就好了"},{"pid":"c1b03eb1a6df117d13025b2e801dc8d1153a3614","tid":2352141,"uid":16925,"like":66,"dislike":9,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:38:06.000Z","msg":"有屋唔住去訓街已經好無聊，仲要有燈唔用去搞營火燒山"},{"pid":"8a306ddd06e333b307140f75ef499c523f83a362","tid":2352141,"uid":27251,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:38:27.000Z","msg":"香港人垃撚圾無公德心都唔係第一日"},{"pid":"94b2868bef485b1ce5ec01542978e313d4b37b4e","tid":2352141,"uid":77556,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:42:36.000Z","msg":"咁死得啦 呢排啲KOL仲係咁推露營<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Q1or2OngX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Q1or2OngX0&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=58c18dd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Q1or2OngX0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇黎成個郊外都會被啲冇公得心嘅人玩死"},{"pid":"8a0ab70609fccff309effe07c270cda4f657bb99","tid":2352141,"uid":67910,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"94b2868bef485b1ce5ec01542978e313d4b37b4e","tid":2352141,"uid":77556,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:42:36.000Z","msg":"咁死得啦 呢排啲KOL仲係咁推露營<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Q1or2OngX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Q1or2OngX0&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=58c18dd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Q1or2OngX0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇黎成個郊外都會被啲冇公得心嘅人玩死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:44:05.000Z","msg":"去唔緊要 做返自己本份 唔好搞死個郊外 自然環境"},{"pid":"21d48d348ddbf6dd7c5234919ba1bd9603e62e5a","tid":2352141,"uid":183601,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"94b2868bef485b1ce5ec01542978e313d4b37b4e","tid":2352141,"uid":77556,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:42:36.000Z","msg":"咁死得啦 呢排啲KOL仲係咁推露營<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Q1or2OngX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%